tournament.name: MN Gate Fair 2023
tournament.registration_message: Join MPLS Killer Queen for our annual summer Invitational, now hosted at Can Can Wonderland. This massive arcade is filled with Artist-designed mini golf, vintage pinball, new and retro games, multiple bars and a full kitchen offering boozy milkshakes and great food, all while supporting the local arts community, including local art for sale on site. This incredible new venue will offer multiple Killer Queen cabs in a private cocktail lounge with ample seating. 32 team soft cap with an Indie Game Tourney, Mixer Draft and other events planned for the weekend.

This massive arcade is filled with Artist-designed mini golf, vintage pinball, new and retro games, multiple bars and a full kitchen offering boozy milkshakes and great food, all while supporting the local arts community, including local art for sale on site. This incredible new venue will offer multiple Killer Queen cabs in a private cocktail lounge with ample seating. 32 team soft cap with an Indie Game Tourney, Mixer Draft and other events planned for the weekend.

This massive arcade is filled with Artist-designed mini golf, vintage pinball, new and retro games, multiple bars and a full kitchen offering boozy milkshakes and great food, all while supporting the local arts community, including local art for sale on site. This incredible new venue will offer multiple Killer Queen cabs in a private cocktail lounge with ample seating. 32 team soft cap with an Indie Game Tourney, Mixer Draft and other events planned for the weekend.
